     H            Y.
     F** UTLR54 ****************************************************
     F*  UTILITY - UTILITY - RETRIEVE CONS PARENT FROM CHILD P/S#  *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)                                         *
     F*           05/01/2017                                       *
     F*------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR54'
     F*                    PARM           $BAR1   9
     F*                    PARM           $BAR2   9
     F*                    PARM           $ODRN  10
     F*                    PARM           $ASN   10
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $BAR1   9   CHILD PACKING LIST#
     F*   OUT $BAR2   9   PARENT PACKING LIST#
     F*       $ODRN  10   PARENT PO#
     F*       $ASN   10   PARENT ASN#
     F*       $RTN    1   RETURN
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PL79 IF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     E                    DAT        10  1
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     C                     EXSR #INZ
     C                     Z-ADD0         K@BIN   20
      * CHAIN AB#PP78
     C           $BAR1     CHAINAB#PL79              98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C           P8SKJY    ANDEQ'C'
     C           P8FLD4    ANDNE*BLANK
     C                     MOVELP8FLD4    $BAR2
     C                     MOVELP8FLD1    $ODRN
     C                     MOVELP8FLD3    $ASN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           $BAR2     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     C           #INZ      BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $BAR1   9
     C                     PARM           $BAR2   9
     C                     PARM           $ODRN  10
     C                     PARM           $ASN   10
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $BAR2
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
